{"tid":1136532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那霸道迫害宗教！ 山東第一觀音像遭整容成孔子","createTime":"2019-05-03T05:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T08:50:02.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"72d23adaf4de7bc6a42af1663b86e0820fae7e4a","tid":1136532,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpU8QDfD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpU8QDfD.jpg&h=d371889d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpVT8xrt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpVT8xrt.jpg&h=6e544fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨政府主張無神論，持續迫害宗教信仰自由，先前炸毀全球最高的「滴水觀音」像，最近將「山東第一觀音」聖泉觀音整容成儒家孔子像，原本白色的觀音像現在已經面目全非，變成一座黑漆漆的孔子像。<br />\n<br />\n長期關注中國人權問題的《寒冬》雜誌報導，事件發生在山東平度市開發區城東埠村的聖水池民俗文化園，2011年耗資200多萬元人民幣（約新台幣917萬元）雕刻這尊高21公尺的大理石聖泉觀音像，此觀音像被稱為「山東第一觀音」，村民及遊客經常來此燒香祈福。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，2018年秋天，中國政府下令，不允許傳播封建迷信，信佛、拜觀音都是不被允許的，所以聖泉觀音像必須被拆除，但村民不捨銷毀觀音像，所以有人發想出「奇招」，將觀音像加以「整容」，保留觀音身但換上孔子的頭，「聖泉觀音」4個字和觀音底座的蓮花都被打磨掉，觀音左手上的玉淨瓶改成了竹簡，整個雕像的顏色也由原來的白色換成了古銅色，理由是孔子屬於中國傳統文化的聖人，紀念孔聖人就不是「迷信」。<br />\n<br />\n許多村民看到荒唐的合體像憤恨不已，有人說，現在像回到毛澤東時代，不讓人信神、信佛，只許人信共產黨。"},{"pid":"2fdbd8d858e0259d7d1d757800cd93065831841c","tid":1136532,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377f75986cfdd2e97542cd82d737e254e4139e9f","tid":1136532,"uid":103230,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"孔子坐蓮"},{"pid":"e55c54f4f0a26e4473a3737a90b0a462fd138db2","tid":1136532,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:35:30.000Z","msg":"好似地獄樂入面d怪物咁"},{"pid":"77b989ba79ca00ca9c1f1b8c5a686447d7dbb98a","tid":1136532,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"377f75986cfdd2e97542cd82d737e254e4139e9f","tid":1136532,"uid":103230,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"孔子坐蓮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef8b6bc95b14000f09ecac65d4a231301322913","tid":1136532,"uid":68132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"頭大身細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20002789e3df3929aa69621fc1848dc0890bef40","tid":1136532,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee334e77668cae62c1a8cc47f535375915fcd49","tid":1136532,"uid":221346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"孔子米9都變到侏儒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a868f3eea454d25c39d32f1105f1755ae5b1fe5e","tid":1136532,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:31:49.000Z","msg":"勁似P圖"},{"pid":"353999c747051365a1d4c6d04329d7239f427666","tid":1136532,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"觀音都唔得<br />\n佛得唔得？"},{"pid":"b6322361d77519851cf032d550169fb5cfb31014","tid":1136532,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"353999c747051365a1d4c6d04329d7239f427666","tid":1136532,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"觀音都唔得<br />\n佛得唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:50:02.000Z","msg":"要歷史上存在<br />\n即係可以信耶穌<br />\n唔可以信上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}